(30, NULL, 407, '17408298531978.pdf', 'Passenger', 'Skoda', 2, 'Wexford', 'Riverchapel Co Wexford', NULL, 'Riverchapel Co Wexford', 'T12 R68V', 0, 'Scala', '2020', 'Saloon', 'Diesel', '1', '1.6L', 'BEIGE', '4', '3', '7', 17900, NULL, '2030-03-30', '2030-03-29', 'Here we have my rare black edition Scala. It has many extras from that came with the car as standard. Such as the black wheels and tinted windows.\r\nIt is in Immaculate condition.\r\n2keys.\r\nTax 09/25\r\nVery low milage.\r\n92,000km ( 57,000 miles )\r\nThe rare ŌĆśblackŌĆÖ edition.\r\nI now have a company car, so the Scala is up for sale.\r\nFull service history\r\nLast serviced 30/4/24 at 88.284km.\r\nThe 2020 Skoda Scala Black Edition 1.6 TDI has a 115 horsepower turbocharged diesel engine. It also has a number of features, including:\r\nLane assist:\r\nLED headlightsTinted rear windows:\r\nElectric windows:\r\nElectric mirrors:\r\nCruise control:\r\nDual zone climate control:\r\nUSB-C charging ports:\r\nEight-inch touchscreen:\r\nTinted rear windows:\r\nElectric windows:\r\nElectric mirrors:\r\nCruise control:\r\nI am in Riverchapel Co Wexford.', '174082982275461jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, '1', 3, 0, 0, '2026-06-17 07:21:42', 0, '2025-03-01 11:41:24', '2026-06-17 07:21:42'),
