(489, 1, 407, 'Cork', 'Centre 30', 'Centre 30', 'Oliver Plunkett Stre', 'T12 R68V', 0, NULL, NULL, 0, 370, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, 'weekly', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 'Apartment', '2025-03-12', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, NULL, 1, 1, 0, 2, 2, 'A2', '', 0, 1, '3 years', NULL, '[\"Washing Machine\",\"Patio\",\"Full Furnished\",\"Tennis Court\"]', 'Welcome to 14 The Avenue, built in 2002 this C1 BER rated three-bedroom semidetached home is located in Green Valley, Donnybrook. This home comes to the market in need of modernisation throughout. There is a great blend of both living and bedroom accommodation. Upon entering you are greeted with a living room, kitchen with dining area, downstairs WC. Over head are two double bedrooms, single bedroom and family bathroom. The property is conveniently located only a short distance from Douglas Village while also being easily accessible to schools, shops, restaurants, bus routes, sports clubs and all local amenities. The property is within easy reach of Cork Airport and other major employment hubs such as Cork city centre, Ringaskiddy and Little Island and the South Link Road network. This is a great opportunity for first time buyers and those trading down who are looking in this highly popular area.\r\nViewing is highly advised to fully appreciate what this home has to offer!', NULL, '174082374634662jfif', NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 0, 2, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 35, '2025-03-01 09:51:43', '2025-04-15 03:42:58'),
